<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> no, haste plays no part in the ratio of weapons. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Though the game engine calculates haste as a % increase (FBSS is 21% not 17. CoF is 36, not 31, and Speed of Shissar is 66%), this translates into hitting faster. You don't even need a parse to see the obvious effects of being fully hasted.  Without full haste (or any haste at all) I can actually read something soembody tells me without using the combat box. With full haste, I am spamming too fast to read ANYTHING that goes by.<br>
<br>
Fact is, it's very difficult to judge just how well a weapon is going to do using a formula, because there are a lot of variables in how much damage you will do.<br>
<br>
13/20 &gt; 15/25, barely.  It's a good enough difference to main hand 13/20 and not worry about swapping them around.  So, it stands to reason that 15/22 will out-damage 13/20, simply because you are going to get a decent increase in the straight up melee. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uashbaneswiftdagger.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ashbane Swiftdagger</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/19/02 4:08:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10773.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: 15/22 or 13/20?</span><hr size=1> my head hurts,  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udietrichsoulpiercer.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dietrich SoulPiercer</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/19/02 5:02:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10773.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: 15/22 or 13/20?</span><hr size=1> If your a level 60 rogue the +5 % piercing on reis works out to +3 skill points. About equal to 12 atk...which is rougly equal to a 1.2% increase in piercing dmg.<br>
